#Commit message standard 
feat(login): add token-based authentication support
fix(api): resolve null response handling in user service
refactor(framework): move common locators to base page
test(regression): add checkout flow validation tests

Most Common Commit Types
Type	Usage
feat	New feature
fix	Bug fix
refactor	Code improvement without behavior change
test	Adding/updating tests
docs	Documentation
chore	Dependency/config/build updates
style	Formatting only
perf	Performance optimization
ci	CI/CD pipeline changes
